task.summary: Fixed path to demo_cell in cell_builder
Changed format for mechanisms in Cell.create and in demo neuron files
Changed variable name filename to model_dir in class Cell()

Set celsius in hoc
Before celsius had no effect on runs of the cell.

Changed parameters: l, ra for Section to upper case
NEURON parameters need to have the same name in python in order to be applied.

Changed demo directory
Now demo is directly in folder cell_fitting.

New function in Class Cell: get_attr()
Cell.get_attr(self,keys) allows the access of an attribute of Cell by a list of keys (same as used for update_attr)
Changed :type specifications to lower case for python build-in types

New function in Section Class: play_current
The function play_current can be used to play a vector containing the current at each time step into a cell during a simulation.

First version of the optimizer
Optimizer can be used for fitting cells with evoluationary multi-objective optimization to experimental data.
Add demo cells and data for testing and demonstrating code

Changed init of Section
Sections are now initialized with the parameter geom instead of L, diam to allow to change between the L, diam and the pt3dadd representation of the geometry.

Changed Section init and added test function test_morph
Section was changed to allow the definition of morphology by either L and diam or by 3D and diam coordinates. The function test_morph plots the morphology of a cell.

Changed update_attr() method of Cell
The method update_attr() is now able to add new paths to params defined by keys if they did not existed yet.
Method substitute_section as method from Cell
